# Vercel Web Analytics Implementation

## Summary
Successfully installed and configured Vercel Web Analytics for this Next.js App Router project.

## Changes Made

### 1. Installed Dependencies
- **@vercel/analytics** (v1.6.1): Main analytics package
- Also fixed missing dependencies that were causing build failures:
  - @radix-ui/react-collapsible (v1.1.12)
  - @radix-ui/react-use-controllable-state (v1.2.2)
  - cmdk (v1.1.1)
  - framer-motion (v12.34.3)
