### 2. Modified Files

#### app/layout.tsx
- Added import: `import { Analytics } from '@vercel/analytics/next';`
- Added `<Analytics />` component inside the `<body>` tag, after the Toaster components
- The component is placed at the root layout level to track analytics across all pages

#### package.json
- Updated dependencies to include @vercel/analytics and other missing packages
- Package manager: Using pnpm (lockfile: pnpm-lock.yaml)

## Implementation Details

The Analytics component was added to the root layout file (app/layout.tsx) as this is a Next.js App Router project. The component is placed inside the `<body>` tag after the existing UI components (Toaster, SonnerToast), which is the recommended position according to Vercel's documentation.

## Verification

- ✅ Build completed successfully with `pnpm run build`
- ✅ No TypeScript errors
- ✅ Analytics component properly integrated in the root layout
- ✅ Lock file (pnpm-lock.yaml) updated with new dependencies

